Gratitude to " @madeinargentinalv " for graciously allowing the display of my artwork in your esteemed restaurant.

Although Miami is my birthplace, my familial ties to Argentina foster a meaningful connection with the local Argentinian community. Argentina, a truly exquisite country, captivated me during a three-month stay at the age of 21. The cuisine and architecture left a lasting impression, and the warmth of the people added to the experience.

This painting draws inspiration from Argentina's recent World Cup triumph, a time coinciding with my residency in Miami. The entire city buzzed with excitement as Messi joined our team, Inter-Miami. The original painting is available for purchase, and I offer limited edition prints as well. For inquiries, kindly contact me directly. Thank you.

About brand 🔸🔸🔸
RazielGates, a Miami-born pop artist now based in Las Vegas, creates captivating artwork that embodies the pulse of exciting pop culture and showcases original designs through the medium of collage art and MixedMedia Art. Currently, the artwork is undergoing a transformative journey into various forms, including clothing, skateboards, hats, and installation art pieces.

Next challenge🔸🔸🔸
My upcoming venture involves crafting a hyped cultural clothing experience, akin to the essence of brands like Supreme or BAPE, as my objective. I aspire to create a product that not only imparts the sensation of donning exclusive art but also serves as a destination for individuals from varied backgrounds, cultures, music influences, and diverse interests.

Business story in three sentences🔸🔸🔸

Persist in diligent effort, even when met with skepticism from others.

Navigate through challenges, working within an environment where doubt surrounds you.

Maintain unwavering self-belief, as eventually, your talents will garner recognition from everyone.
